### Kaptai Tourist API — request collection
# IntelliJ / VS Code "REST Client" format. Every route is nested under an
# `Accept: application/json` predicate, so that header is always required.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090/api/v1
@hotelId = 1111

### Public — browse all hotels (no token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotel
Accept: application/json

### Public — get one hotel by id (no token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotel/{{hotelId}}
Accept: application/json
